    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="letter">
                <div type="text">
                    <opener>
                        <placeName>16 Hart Str.</placeName>
                        <date>April 10 1841</date>
                        <salute>My dear Henslow</salute>
                    </opener>
                    <div type="transcription">
                        <p>The best thanks I can give you for your extract from Liebig will I am sure be to say that I have just sent it to the press to improve a reprint of my Elements when touching on cavern deposits. I am much obliged for your pamphlet on Wheat &amp; hope you are getting on with fossil botany.</p>
                        <p>My wife joins in kind remembrance to you &amp; Mrs Henslow &amp; believe me</p>
                        <p>very faithfully</p>
                        <p>Cha Lyell</p>
                        <p>Darwin is only going on in the same state</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </body>
